Clone the repo:

git clone https://github.com/yourusername/blockdag-scripts.git
cd blockdag-scripts


Configure wallet:

Option A: .env file

PUB_ETH_ADDR=0xYourEvmWalletAddress


Option B: wallet.txt (last line used)

0xYourEvmWalletAddress


.env takes precedence if both exist.

Verify Docker:

docker --version
docker compose version


Install Docker on Ubuntu/WSL:

sudo ./install_docker.sh

▶️ Running the Node
./blockdag.sh


Check status:

docker ps
tail -f bin/bdag/logs/node.log


Stop node:

docker compose down
